<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.155286>
    dc:description "FIGURE 15. Mooreonuphis nunezi sp. nov. Paratype (MNCN 16.01 / 3330). Line drawings. A, parapodium chaetiger 1, anterior view; B, parapodium chaetiger 34, anterior view; C, bidentate long-appendaged pseudocompound hook from chaetiger 1; D, tridentate long-appendaged pseudocompound hook from chaetiger 1; E, tridentate short-appendaged pseudocompound hook from chaetiger 2; F, simple large median hook from chaetiger 1; G, tridentate short-appendaged pseudocompound hook from chaetiger 5; H, compound limbate (= spiniger) from chaetiger 6; pectinate chaeta from the same; J, aciculae from chaetiger 1; K, aciculae from chaetiger 8; L, aciculae from chaetiger 14; M, maxillae." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "http://zenodo.org/record/155286/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.155275>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Onuphis augeneri sp. nov. Holotype A (ZMH V. 868), paratype B-H (ZMH P 27820). Line drawings. A, detailed view of prostomium; B, parapodium chaetiger 1, anterior view; C, parapodium chaetiger 3, anterior view; D, E, shortappendaged bidentate pseudocompound hooks of chaetiger 1; F, short-appendaged tridentate pseudocompound hook of chaetiger 1; G, slender long-appendaged bidentate pseudocompound hook of chaetiger 1; H, maxillae." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "http://zenodo.org/record/155275/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

